The universe, in its infinite, baffling wisdom, demands order. Or at least, the appearance of it. This particular article chronicles the individuals tasked with maintaining that illusion for the [United States Army](/United_States_Army): the [Adjutant General of the United States Army](/Adjutant_General_of_the_United_States_Army). It’s a role that, despite its seemingly bureaucratic nature, has been the quiet, meticulous backbone of the military establishment for centuries. One might even call it essential, if one were prone to such enthusiastic declarations.

### The Adjutant General of the United States Army

---
